  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/91689cbbf486ba54e94532fc42e83f99.poster.avif?t=1639751293\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/91689cbbf486ba54e94532fc42e83f99.webm?t=1639751293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/91689cbbf486ba54e94532fc42e83f99.mp4?t=1639751293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Enjoy a 3 VS 3 street soccer game with players all around the world!<br>'Extreme Soccer' is a competitive online multiplayer soccer(futsal) game that offers the excitement of a 3 VS 3 match.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/5328eac2db3d4ea87aeae602d853d767.poster.avif?t=1639751293\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/5328eac2db3d4ea87aeae602d853d767.webm?t=1639751293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/5328eac2db3d4ea87aeae602d853d767.mp4?t=1639751293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong> ■ Dynamic physics engine: </strong><br>-Try dynamic gameplay through intelligent passes using the surrounding walls.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/dc646937be4da70dda03e0e3c6552b1e.poster.avif?t=1639751293\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/dc646937be4da70dda03e0e3c6552b1e.webm?t=1639751293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/dc646937be4da70dda03e0e3c6552b1e.mp4?t=1639751293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong> ■ Attractive players: </strong><br>-Enjoy spectacular play with players with special abilities!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/88949c765426bbadbf12bc1493add033.poster.avif?t=1639751293\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/88949c765426bbadbf12bc1493add033.webm?t=1639751293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/88949c765426bbadbf12bc1493add033.mp4?t=1639751293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong> ■ 3v3 team play: </strong><br>-Invite your friends to play as a team!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/913cc4d35afd80baff65dba5eafad5a3.poster.avif?t=1639751293\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/913cc4d35afd80baff65dba5eafad5a3.webm?t=1639751293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477730/extras/913cc4d35afd80baff65dba5eafad5a3.mp4?t=1639751293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong> ■ Charming outfits: </strong><br>You can collect and customize unique outfits.",
